## Installation and set up

1. Clone the repo
2. Install [NVM](https://github.com/creationix/nvm) (Node Version Manager)
3. Install Node 6.3.0 - `nvm install v6.3.0`. This supports most of the features of ES6 natively - [http://node.green](http://node.green)
4. Run `npm install` to install server-side, client-side and development dependencies. See `dependencies` and `devDependencies` in `package.json` for a list (it's long.)
5. Run `npm run dev` to boot the app. This is configured along with other scripts in your `package.json`.
6. **Bonus** - Install [AVN](https://github.com/wbyoung/avn) for automatic version switching - `npm install -g avn avn-nvm`

## Building and Running Production Server

```bash
npm run build
npm run start
```
